{"tid":410931,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"歐洲太空總署：2030開始殖民月球","createTime":"2017-09-23T11:18:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-24T01:57:24.000Z","uid":89134,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a5514b02d554bff137d1a27f5d6c00253c1186f2","tid":410931,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T11:18:44.000Z","msg":"歐洲太空總署（ESA）周日（17日）起在拉脫維亞首都里加召開歐洲行星科學大會，預測到2030年會由少數科學家等技術人員初步殖民月球，更指幾十年後「可能會有小孩在月球出生」。<br />\n<br />\n負責策劃「月球村」計劃的大使富萬（Bernard Foing）於會上透露，初步計劃派6至10名科學家和工程師等人到月球。富萬形容，情況就如發展鐵路一樣，有了車站就會有村莊圍着它發展，商業活動亦應運而生。他相信直到2040年，殖民月球的人數能增至100人，到2050年規模更可能擴張過至千人。<br />\n<br />\n由於國際太空站將於2024年退役，ESA認為建立月球村可作為延續太空站的下一個項目。雖然科學家和商業探礦者都對計劃表示有興趣，但此概念尚未證明有其市場需求，以吸引政治領袖支持。<br />\n<br />\n唔知咁多位連登炒家有冇興趣到時炒上月球既位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72f399f0ddcba9d66502c87ab816a2dc37129f91","tid":410931,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T11:19:36.000Z","msg":"宇宙世紀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4a917b7e0aefd6de89987a019eb21bd46f81ea5","tid":410931,"uid":35348,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T11:52:26.000Z","msg":"馮&middot;布朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10c796773b989793e0f458674382eb4613867ee1","tid":410931,"uid":57303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T11:53:35.000Z","msg":"星球大戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55f26d0bd31991765bc17385bbd2424c3f248b2e","tid":410931,"uid":97451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T11:57:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"008bf60a109ac8f6a0a8b8af770e9a19238ba872","tid":410931,"uid":97465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T11:58:13.000Z","msg":"球蝗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8088845e0c093b9fe7429fcdb9c7a1afee19958","tid":41093